snippet.title: Gun Jam | PC Date Announcement Trailer | Available April 19
snippet.description:
Gun Jam releases on Steam (PC) on April 19 - Wishlist Gun Jam here https://store.steampowered.com/app/1308360/GUN_JAM/

Created by Jaw Drop Games and published by Raw Fury, Gun Jam is a rhythm-action FPS where you must shoot, dash and kick to the beat to survive. It features a unique beat-pattern shooting mechanic, a multi-genre OST, custom music and firefights with hordes of enemies in a vibrant world. Prepare to obliterate enemies whilst blasting to the beat.

Discord - https://discord.com/invite/meWGuTk8MU
Website - https://www.gunjamgame.com/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/gunjamgame
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@gunjamgame
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/gunjamgame
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/gunjamgame/
